name: Envio de mensaje para contacto exitoso

testSteps.description: Given el usuario visitante se encuentra en la pagina de Contact us

children.description: Visitor clicks on Contact Us option in home

testSteps.description: When llena la informacion de los campos obligatorios y valida su accion

children.description: Visitor fill required contact us fields
Visitor selects 1 in Subeject heading option
Visitor enters 'errol.olson@yahoo.com' into Contact us email field
Visitor enters 'Est sint qui qui. Natus nulla cupiditate error aut. Sed sunt minus qui.' into Contact us message field
Visitor clicks on Submit to send the message

testSteps.description: Then aparece un mensaje de envio exitoso

children.description: Then the sent message was successful should be 'Your message has been successfully sent to our team.'
